title: Friday Football Feast!
description: Preseason has begun! PA is joined by Paul Charchian to discuss the upcoming Vikings season, injuries and all. MN Native and Golf.com's Josh Berhow, former NFL player Ross Tucker, and Troy Renck of KMGH-TV in Denver call in!
